race.comment: GLACIELE (1) is a speedy colt who placed at both runs in first campaign. Ticking over well with a couple of trials and returns with the blinkers . Expected to feature again. TAYLOR'S RAGE (9) is a filly who placed half of six starts so far. Paced 2/3 fresh and only try course and distance. Looks well placed here. Two first starters in the race and both are trialling well. MISS MCLAREN (2) is a four-year-old mare who has won her last three trials and should be ready to fire. ELIZAHRO (3) is a filly by Astern and is unbeaten in two trials so far. Tricky gate but showing ability. SOUTHAMPTON NICCO (12) has been thereabouts over further last couple but has solid figures this sharper dash. Senior rider goes on and worth another try.
